article_id:312,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing Gala Dragalia!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia will start <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1553666400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>What is Gala Dragalia?</div><div>・The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers, dragons, and wyrmprints will be increased to 6%, up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div>・Limited-time Gala Dragalia versions of adventurers will be added, available only while Gala Dragalia is active!</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1553666400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1554011940"></span></div><div><br></div><div>The featured Gala Dragalia adventurer is detailed below.</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia adventurer:</div><div><div class="summonPickUp">
